data.text: Staunton City Schools believes that the greatest asset to the teaching profession are our PEOPLE! That is each of YOU! Every time we grow in the profession, our students also grow! This why we are so invested in focused teacher and student initiatives including: Professional development days, SCS University, New Teacher Training, collaborative student success plans, and college/career plans. Here you will find information about working for Staunton Public Schools
